$ Python library: deep_translator
@ deep_translator

code {
$ sudo pip install -U deep-translator
code }

Translate a German sentence to english:
code {
from deep_translator import GoogleTranslator
translator=GoogleTranslator(source='de', target='en')
print(translator.translate('Kinder, das Essen wird kalt!'))
code }

sa:
  The Python libraries `→ development/languages/Python/libraries/googletrans` and `→ development/languages/Python/libraries/translators`.
